## 1.7.3    Institutional arrangements to facilitate the implementation of the activities

Institutional arrangements to facilitate the implementation of the activities (ครั้งก่อนยังไม่ได้ให้ข้อมูล)

·       coordination mechanisms (e.g. interministerial committees)

·       financial mechanisms (e.g. domestic climate funds that finance action to address loss and damage)

·       mechanisms for collecting, storing and analysing data related to loss and damage (e.g. periodic assessments, databases)

·       stakeholder engagement mechanisms (e.g. forums, stakeholder platforms)

·       mechanisms for evaluating efforts to address loss and damage (e.g. independent evaluation committees)

**Dedicated Section:** Ensure a dedicated, structured section is included, as required by the MPGs, to report on L&D

**Mechanism Reporting:** Detail the national mechanisms (e.g., early warning systems, disaster risk financing, social protection) used to avert, minimize, and address L&D

อยากได้ส่วน Finance needs ด้วย ในการลดความสูญเสียและเสียหาย
